graph TB
    subgraph "RHOAI Operator (rhods-operator)"
        DSCController[DataScienceCluster Controller]
        DSCIController[DSCInitialization Controller]
        WebhookServer[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        SecretGen[SecretGenerator Controller]
        CertGen[CertConfigMapGenerator Controller]
        ComponentReconcilers[Component Reconcilers<br/>Dashboard, KServe, ModelMesh, etc.]

        DSCController -->|coordinates| ComponentReconcilers
        DSCIController -->|initializes| MonitoringStack
        WebhookServer -->|validates/mutates| DSCController
        WebhookServer -->|validates/mutates| DSCIController
        SecretGen -->|generates| Secrets[Component Secrets]
        CertGen -->|generates| CertConfigMaps[TLS ConfigMaps]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        DSC[DataScienceCluster CR]
        DSCI[DSCInitialization CR]
        FeatureTracker[FeatureTracker CR]
    end

    subgraph "Platform Infrastructure"
        MonitoringStack[Monitoring Stack<br/>Prometheus, Alertmanager]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Integration]
        TrustedCA[Trusted CA Bundles]
        PlatformNamespaces[Generated Namespaces]
    end

    subgraph "Managed Components"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        Workbenches[Jupyter Workbenches]
        KServe[KServe]
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh]
        Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines]
        CodeFlare[CodeFlare]
        Ray[Ray Operator]
        Kueue[Kueue]
        TrainingOp[Training Operator]
        TrustyAI[TrustyAI]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| DSC
    User -->|creates| DSCI

    DSC -->|watched by| DSCController
    DSCI -->|watched by| DSCIController

    DSCController -->|deploys| Dashboard
    DSCController -->|deploys| Workbenches
    DSCController -->|deploys| KServe
    DSCController -->|deploys| ModelMesh
    DSCController -->|deploys| Pipelines
    DSCController -->|deploys| CodeFlare
    DSCController -->|deploys| Ray
    DSCController -->|deploys| Kueue
    DSCController -->|deploys| TrainingOp
    DSCController -->|deploys| TrustyAI
    DSCController -->|deploys| ModelRegistry

    DSCIController -->|configures| ServiceMesh
    DSCIController -->|configures| TrustedCA
    DSCIController -->|creates| PlatformNamespaces

    DSCController -->|tracks| FeatureTracker

    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server] -->|calls webhook| WebhookServer
    DSCController -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    DSCIController -->|manages resources| K8sAPI

    PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator] -->|scrapes| MonitoringStack

